    <h2>Date Field Restrictions</h2>

    <p>Use the min and max attributes to add restrictions to dates:</p>

    <form action="/action_page.php">
        <label for="datemin">Enter a data que nasceu:</label>
        <input type="date" id="datemin" name="datemin" min="2000-01-02"><br><br>

        <label for="datemax">Enter a data atualmente:</label>
        <input type="date" id="datemax" name="datemax" max="2025-12-31"><br><br>

        <input type="submit" value="confirmar">
    </form>
</body>

